<h4 id="_2-2-3-任务的拾取和完成" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-2-3-任务的拾取和完成" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 2.2.3 任务的拾取和完成</h4>
<p>  然后完成任务的查询拾取和处理操作</p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token doc-comment comment">/**
