ber"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>如果从网关出去的线所有条件都不满足的情况下会抛出系统异常，</p>
<p><img src="@source/notes/record/Flowable入门-高级篇/assets/image-20220326104744181.png" alt="image-20220326104744181"></p>
<p>但是要注意任务没有结束，还是原来的任务，我们可以重置流程变量</p>
<div class="language-java line-numbers-mode" data-ext="java"><pre v-pre class="language-java"><code><span class="token annotation punctuation">@Test</span>
